export function toFloatType( type ) {

	if ( /^(i?int)$/.test( type ) ) return 'float';

	const vecMatch = /^(i|u)?vec([234])$/.exec( type );

	if ( vecMatch ) return 'vec' + vecMatch[ 2 ];

	return type;

}
